Ya.

74
00:04:19,545 --> 00:04:21,096
<i>Walau baru sekali bertemu,</i>

75
00:04:22,632 --> 00:04:24,016
<i>itu cukup bagiku.</i>

76
00:04:25,801 --> 00:04:28,270
Aku memang ingin mencari pekerja lagi.

77
00:04:28,971 --> 00:04:30,356
Apa alasannya?

78
00:04:30,723 --> 00:04:32,358
<i>Orang yang ingin kuandalkan.</i>

79
00:04:33,434 --> 00:04:35,027
