168
00:10:25,411 --> 00:10:26,587
Aku tak bisa.

169
00:10:31,667 --> 00:10:33,886
Apa alasanmu ingin kerja di sini?

170
00:10:37,673 --> 00:10:39,016
Naluriku.

171
00:10:40,593 --> 00:10:42,060
Naluri?

172
00:10:44,096 --> 00:10:45,564
Aku merasa

