Naluriku bilang begitu.

175
00:11:07,244 --> 00:11:08,420
Terdengar menarik.

176
00:11:09,330 --> 00:11:10,881
Apa?

177
00:11:16,545 --> 00:11:17,930
Dengar, Semuanya.

178
00:11:18,297 --> 00:11:21,350
Mulai sekarang, anak ini, Jo Yi-seo,

179
00:11:28,682 --> 00:11:30,359
adalah manajer DanBam.

180
00:11:41,278 --> 00:11:42,704
Beri selamat.

181
00:11:55,826 --> 00:11:57,977
<font color="#ffff00">PERUSAHAAN JANGGA</font>

182
00:11:57,978 --> 00:11:59,145
<font color="#ffff00">DAFTAR PEMEGANG SAHAM</font>

183
